spec_data.Name: perl-XML-NamespaceSupport
spec_data.Description:
This module offers a simple to process name-spaced XML names (unames) from
within any application that may need them. It also helps maintain a prefix
to name space URI map, and provides a number of basic checks.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 06:31:22 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A simple generic name space support class
